{"tid":1385330,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［真人真事］港豬同事表示今朝塞鐵好爽","createTime":"2019-07-30T05:03:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T06:07:36.000Z","uid":111694,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9126d35980d93c473e86a7cc8767b2ebf342bc3a","tid":1385330,"uid":111694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:03:40.000Z","msg":"話說港豬同事明明尋晚就收到風調景嶺會有行動，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">但</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢唔信亦都唔覺得會搞得成</span></span></strong>，最後走左去搭鐵塞左一粒鐘，然後決定<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">返屋企</span></span>home office!<br />\n<br />\n本身仲聽到佢好多怨言<strong>（唔好搞到我 我淨係想返工 下刪一千）</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">但！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n一返到去home office，佢就表示好撚爽，可以扮工扮到夜晚12點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">事實證明</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意根本唔會逆轉</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n因為港豬根本就係順民， 要得到佢地既支持其實好簡單 - <strong>就係飼料！！</strong><br />\n<br />\n而交通癱瘓根本就係比佢地可以輕鬆賺取飼料既方法！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當然有人亦會話比佢地home office到咁我地咪失敗，因為無法癱瘓香港經濟。但你諗下港豬大條道理罷工，只會按章工作，<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">我地一樣比到壓力班商家佬</span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n所以我地而家要做既，就只係一次成功癱瘓香港交通運輸，全港黎一次大罷工！！亦已經有人開po講緊策略<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383431\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383431</a><br />\n<br />\n［gold]<strong>和理非一定要係8/5做到野，唔可以要勇武血白流！</strong>[/gold]！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"fd027ffda794aa171d60818470e589eec8259b14","tid":1385330,"uid":266279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:07:50.000Z","msg":"8.5 全民三罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5cbe7924be70e956912576ce10355e99456b46","tid":1385330,"uid":111694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:14:33.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"2278f4954248d4a4bc101e47400340a7c0e8eea2","tid":1385330,"uid":111694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:52:52.000Z","msg":"單機推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d9beb088306beb5676cb7ba0d37be33968c37a","tid":1385330,"uid":290991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:59:22.000Z","msg":"唔好阻到我 阻到我我實係度門同你還拖返一兩個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7602eaf4fd5f0d81c604f8d1131251aeb3f16460","tid":1385330,"uid":111694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33d9beb088306beb5676cb7ba0d37be33968c37a","tid":1385330,"uid":290991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:59:22.000Z","msg":"唔好阻到我 阻到我我實係度門同你還拖返一兩個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:05:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁要邀請隻揪sir"},{"pid":"4b521c9dfdd85633a679f57ca62dcde55d75d10e","tid":1385330,"uid":290991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7602eaf4fd5f0d81c604f8d1131251aeb3f16460","tid":1385330,"uid":111694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33d9beb088306beb5676cb7ba0d37be33968c37a","tid":1385330,"uid":290991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:59:22.000Z","msg":"唔好阻到我 阻到我我實係度門同你還拖返一兩個鐘<im